  "description": "Prerequisite: Level 5+ Warlock, Pact of the Blade Invocation\n\nOnce per turn when you hit a creature with your pact weapon, you can expend a Pact Magic spell slot to deal an extra 1d8 Force damage to the target, plus another 1d8 per level of the spell slot, and you can give the target the &amp;Reference[Prone] condition if it is Huge or smaller.\n\nFoundry Note\n\nThe Smite activity consumes a Pact Magic spell slot and increases the damage based on your pact spell level.",
